        AH_A_TIME_OF_GREAT_CHANGE_IS_UPON                                    = 151,  -- Ah, a time of great change is upon us. In a matter of days, the Rites of Succession will be held at the cathedral in Northern San d'Oria. It is then that the new heir to the throne will be decided.
        DUE_TO_THE_UNPREDICTABLE_CIRCUMSTANCES_THAT_TOOK_PLACE               = 152,  -- Due to the unpredictable circumstances that took place at the princess's coming-of-age ceremony, this time, only authorized personnel will be allowed near the proceedings. However, the royal family has requested your services as a guard.
