        IT_WON_T_OPEN                                                        = 6704,  -- It won't open.
        WHAT_S_THIS_THEN_SOMEONE_GAVE_YOU_THIS                               = 6705,  -- What's this, then? Someone gave you this envelope, did they?
        WH_WHAT_IS_THIS                                                      = 6706,  -- Wh-what is this!?
        THIS_RUBBISH_DOES_NOT_FOOL_ME_I_KNOW                                 = 6707,  -- This rubbish does not fool me! I know a forgery when I see one.
        MOST_UNPLEASANT_DO_NOT_SPEAK_TO_ME_OF                                = 6708,  -- Most unpleasant. Do not speak to me of this matter again!
        YOU_CALLED_FOR_ME_YOUR_MAJESTY                                       = 6709,  -- You called for me, Your Majesty?
        FRANCMAGE_I_WAS_NOT_EXPECTING_YOU_SO_SOON                            = 6710,  -- Francmage? I was not expecting you so soon. Monarlais...tell him.
        YES_SIRE                                                             = 6711,  -- Yes, sire.
        FRANCMAGE_I_VE_SUMMONED_YOU_HERE_TODAY_TO                            = 6712,  -- Francmage, I've summoned you here today to talk about one thing--the Northlands investigation.
        OH_YES_THAT_THOSE_BASTOKER_HUMES_ARE_CAUSING                         = 6713,  -- Oh, yes, that. Those Bastoker Humes are causing no end of trouble--saying they want to investigate here, there, and the other place...
        IT_IS_TRUE_THE_HUMES_ARE_FOOLS_AND                                   = 6714,  -- It is true! The Humes are fools, and no better. Can they truly believe that some ancient power lies hidden in that forsaken wasteland?
        HAH_DO_THEY_HOPE_TO_FIND_THE_GATES                                   = 6715,  -- Hah! Do they hope to find the gates to eternal Paradise there, in that lair of fiends most uncouth? Preposterous!
        WE_MUST_TAKE_CONTROL_OF_THIS_SITUATION_IMMEDIATELY                   = 6716,  -- We must take control of this situation immediately. Still, we cannot let them walk about the Northlands freely. Who knows what they're plotting under the guise of this investigation.
        FRANCMAGE_LISTEN_GO_WITH_THE_INVESTIGATION_PARTY_AND                 = 6717,  -- Francmage, listen. Go with the investigation party, and keep a close eye on what our foreign friends do. They are up to something, it is certain.
        I_AM_SURE_NOTHING_WILL_COME_OF_THIS                                  = 6718,  -- I am sure nothing will come of this, but in case they do find something in that wasteland, do not let them take it. Understood?
        AS_YOU_COMMAND_MY_LORD_I_WOULD_GIVE                                  = 6719,  -- As you command, my lord. I would give the very blood that runs in my veins if it were to further the cause of our kingdom. You can rely on me.
        THESE_FOREIGNERS_ARE_WILY_AND_FAITHLESS_NEVER_LET                    = 6720,  -- These foreigners are wily and faithless. Never let down your guard, and may the Goddess of the Dawn protect you in Her mercy.
        THE_KING_HAS_TAKEN_A_BEAUTIFUL_QUEEN_AND                             = 6721,  -- The king has taken a beautiful queen, and I think a splendid addition to the royal family is not far off. An heir, perhaps...
        WE_PEOPLE_OF_SAN_D_ORIA_TOO_MUST                                     = 6722,  -- We people of San d'Oria, too, must ever look to the future. The Elvaan must never fall behind foreigners, in power or faith.
        I_UNDERSTAND_YOUR_GRACE                                              = 6723,  -- I understand, Your Grace.
        VERY_GOOD_DO_WELL_FRANCMAGE                                          = 6724,  -- Very good. Do well, Francmage.
        YES_SIRE_MY_LIFE_FOR_THE_KINGDOM                                     = 6725,  -- Yes, sire! My life for the Kingdom!
        OH_IT_S_YOU_FEAR_NOT_THE_PRECIOUS                                    = 6726,  -- Oh, it's you. Fear not; the precious dragon is not in danger. However, we have learned that Cyranuce is somewhere in the Ghelsba Outpost.
