        AH_NOW_THAT_S_THE_ANSWER_I_WAS                                       = 7413,  -- Ah, now that's the answer I was expectin'. Queen Leaute'd be pleased, she would. You get going, then.
        EH_WHAT_S_THAT_CHANGED_YOUR_MIND_IT                                  = 7414,  -- Eh? What's that? Changed your mind? It be for Queen Leaute, you know!
