        OH_I_KNOW_HOW_SERIOUSLY_YOU_TAKE_YOUR                                = 7441,  -- Oh, I know how seriously you take your duties. Still, though, that rumor troubles me.
        I_WONDER_WOULD_YOU_TAKE_IT_UPON_YOURSELF                             = 7442,  -- I wonder, would you take it upon yourself to look into that matter of my father's ghost in the cathedral?
        OFTEN_WOULD_MY_FATHER_VISIT_THAT_PLACE_PERHAPS                       = 7443,  -- Often would my father visit that place. Perhaps it could be him...
        A_SPIRIT_OF_A_RED_MAGE_ARE_YOU                                       = 7444,  -- A spirit of a red mage? Are you saying my father has returned? And he called my name!? No... How could this be?
        THE_GHOST_GAVE_YOU_SOME_OLD_GREAVES_IN                               = 7445,  -- The ghost gave you some old greaves in return for the watch, did he? Well, let me try putting them on.
        WHAT_NO_OF_COURSE_THEY_RE_NOT_CURSED                                 = 7446,  -- What? No, of course they're not cursed. You should place more trust in my judgment!
