        WHAT_YOU_HAVE_A_SET_OF_GREAVES_THAT                                  = 7452,  -- What, you have a set of greaves that refuses to be worn? I've heard of that sort of thing before. Yes, they had to be taken to the Crawlers' Nest to be exorcised.
