        I_AM_SORRY_CURILLA_BUT_YOU_ARE_SUMMONED                              = 7454,  -- I am sorry, Curilla, but you are summoned for service. The papsque has complained that the regions surrounding San d'Oria are patrolled too thinly. We must think of a plan.
