        YES                                                                  = 7457,  -- Yes...
        A_PITY_I_SAY_WOULD_YOU_BE_INCLINED                                   = 7458,  -- A pity. I say, would you be inclined to take them to the Crawlers' Nest? They must be buried together with % in the place where light shines.
        OF_COURSE_YOU_MAY_DO_WITH_THEM_AS                                    = 7459,  -- Of course, you may do with them as you please. But please, if you do decide to go, come back and tell me how you fared. Even a little information could help solve the puzzle of my father's death.
