        I_COMMEND_YOU_FOR_OFFERING_TO_HELP_BUT                               = 7468,  -- I commend you for offering to help, but already you know as much as I do.
        WHAT_IN_FEI_YIN_YOU_MET_THE_GHOST                                    = 7469,  -- What? In Fei'Yin you met the ghost of my father, and saw him suffering? The mystery deepens.
        YOU_VE_FOUND_MY_FATHER_S_REMAINS_IN                                  = 7470,  -- You've found my father's remains in Garlaige? My poor father's soul will never rest until his remains are properly interred.
        IT_MATTERS_NOT_HOW_MY_FATHER_DIED_NOW                                = 7471,  -- It matters not how my father died... Now I know that ever will his memory live on inside me.
        YOU_WENT_THROUGH_GREAT_LENGTHS_TO_HELP_ME                            = 7472,  -- You went through great lengths to help me. I have never found it easy to express thanks, but know that I will always be grateful.
        EH_WANT_TO_SHOW_ME_YOUR_RING_DO                                      = 7473,  -- Eh? Want to show me your ring, do you? And inscribed upon it are ancient San d'Orian runes? Very well, let us see it.
