        WHILE_WEARING_DURING_A_MATCH_YOU_WILL_BE                             = 8233,  -- While wearing % during a match, you will be able to hear the orders of your nation's Pursuivant. His advice will aid you in battle.
        ALSO_YOU_WILL_BE_INFORMED_OF_ALL_THE                                 = 8234,  -- Also, you will be informed of all the latest match information when entering select cities.
