        IT_APPEARS_YOU_HAVE_PREVIOUSLY_BEEN_ISSUED_A                         = 8462,  -- It appears you have previously been issued a marriage certificate by another nation. The re-issuance of a misplaced certificate can be carried out solely by the officiating body wherefrom it was originally issued.
        IT_APPEARS_YOUR_SPOUSE_S_MARRIAGE_CERTIFICATE_WAS                    = 8463,  -- It appears your spouse's marriage certificate was issued by another nation.
