        ACCEPTING_A_MARRIAGE_CERTIFICATE_FROM_OUR_NATION_WILL                = 8465,  -- Accepting a marriage certificate from our nation will render you ineligible to receive one from another. Furthermore, the nation of issuance for the certificate you hold cannot differ from that of your partner's.
