        MY_COMPANION_AND_I_ARE_UM_SIMPLE_ADVENTURERS                         = 8482,  -- My companion and I are, um...simple adventurers hungry for knowledge. If my lord could spare the time, we wish to learn about the Battle of Xarcabard.
        AH_YOUR_REQUEST_IS_AS_MUSIC_TO_MY                                    = 8483,  -- Ah, your request is as music to my ears, young lady. The youth of today show precious little interest in the events of the past...the sacrifices that many made to ensure the continued existence of our fair Kingdom.
