        IT_IS_CLEAR_THAT_THIS_EMPRESS_NASHMEIRA_TRULY                        = 8519,  -- It is clear that this Empress Nashmeira truly intends to lead her nation to a new age. I have no doubt that she will prove a staunch ally worthy of our trust.
