        HAIL_I_AM_CURILLA_V_MECRU_GENERAL_OF                                 = 8544,  -- Hail! I am Curilla V Mecru, general of the Temple Knights. Our order is charged with protecting Chateau d'Oraguille and the city itself from any forces that would seek to cause chaos inside our fair realm.
        IS_THIS                                                              = 8545,  -- Is this...%?
        YES_IT_IS_TRUE_THAT_I_AM_A                                           = 8546,  -- Yes, it is true that I am a participant in this Trust magic experiment, but I do not recall forming any sort of bond with you.
        PERHAPS_IT_WOULD_BEHOOVE_YOU_TO_FURTHER_SERVE                        = 8547,  -- Perhaps it would behoove you to further serve [your homeland/San d'Oria] before coming to see me.
        WHAT_DO_YOU_WISH_TODAY_OH_YOU_HAVE                                   = 8548,  -- What do you wish today? Oh, you have %? I see...
        SO_YOU_HAVE_SUCCEEDED_IN_DRAWING_FORTH_TRUST                         = 8549,  -- So you have succeeded in drawing forth Trust magic, then.
        NO_I_CANNOT_ADMIT_TO_BEING_SURPRISED_A                               = 8550,  -- No, I cannot admit to being surprised. A man/woman] of your talents is capable of much in these dark times.
        LET_ME_GUESS_YOU_WISH_TO_SEE_IF                                      = 8551,  -- Let me guess--you wish to see if you can summon my alter ego, do you not?
        ATTEMPT_THE_RITUAL_WITH_CURILLA_YES_NO                               = 8552,  -- Attempt the ritual with Curilla? Yes. No.
        I_MUST_CONFESS_MY_HEART_IS_NOT_IN                                    = 8553,  -- I must confess, my heart is not in this, either. Prince Trion insisted that I participate, though, and I cannot deny him.
        BOTH_PRINCE_TRION_AND_THE_JEUNO_INSTITUTE_OF                         = 8554,  -- Both Prince Trion and the Jeuno Institute of Magical Studies had the same words for me when this experiment began.
        THINK_OF_THE_GLORY_CURILLA_YET_TO_BE                                 = 8555,  -- Think of the glory, Curilla. Yet to be honest, I am quite unsure of myself.
        I_FEAR_MY_SKILLS_ARE_YET_INFERIOR_WHAT                               = 8556,  -- I fear my skills are yet inferior. What good can an alter ego be when the original remains weak?
        TRY_AS_I_MIGHT_I_CANNOT_HELP_BUT                                     = 8557,  -- Try as I might, I cannot help but picture people pointing and laughing as I falter. A leader who cannot command respect is no better than a king with no country.
        AND_FURTHER_I_HAVE_NEVER_BEEN_ONE_TO                                 = 8558,  -- And further, I have never been one to fight for fame or personal gain. Not since I lost my eye in exchange for victory in the tourneys.
