        HAHAHAHA_PERHAPS_ONE_DAY_MY_PENMANSHIP_WILL_MATCH                    = 8587,  -- Hahahaha, perhaps one day my penmanship will match my swordsmanship. Fair enough, %, but return to me if ever your mind changes.
