        ANTAGONISTIC_MAY_BE_A_BIT_EXTREME_BUT_IT                             = 8610,  -- Antagonistic may be a bit extreme--but it does describe the feelings I harbored toward you when you bested me in the Stellar Fulcrum. 'Twas truly a match well fought.
