        JEUNO_INSTITUTE_OF_MAGICAL_STUDIES_HAS_DISPATCHED_PERSONNEL          = 8622,  -- [The/I understand that the/I understand that the] Jeuno Institute of Magical Studies has dispatched personnel well-versed in this new initiative to [Southern San d'Oria/Port Bastok/Windurst Woods], so I recommend you speak with them at your earliest convenience.
